io.requery.query

Interface Conditional<Q,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    Q - result of applying the condition
    V - value type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    QueryAttribute<T,V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Abs, AliasedExpression, AttributeBuilder, Avg, Case, Coalesce, Collate, CollectionAttributeBuilder, Count, FieldExpression, Function, ListAttributeBuilder, Lower, MapAttributeBuilder, Max, Min, NamedExpression, Now, ResultAttributeBuilder, Round, SetAttributeBuilder, Sum, Trim, Upper

    public interface Conditional<Q,V>
    Defines an interface for objects for which conditions can be applied to.
